name: Malvern Hills -View From The Beacon - Rocky Hills Canvas Print
description:
Taken on the 16th of March 2013.

Limited run of 100 prints.

In this photo the sun shows the great texture of the rocks on the hills. The still rocks in the foreground produce an eye catching contrast with the snaking shape of the hills in the background.

The photo on canvas is printed on a 100% cotton canvas using pigment based inks, which are colour strong for decades. Giving pictures canvas bright and intense colour production. 

Each canvas is stretched on to a 2cm depth by top quality, kiln-dried wood. The canvases also feature a design which prevents sagging of the material.
